title: BMW X7 M40i.Xdrive.M.Sport 2021
description:
The Brand New 2021 BMW X7 xDrive 40i is now available READT AT DHAKA GULSHAN 

The 2021 BMW X7 is a three-row seven-seater SUV that offers substantial underhood power and a luxurious cabin. In the biggest BMW ever built, there's always room for more. Live at a level above the ordinary in the 2021 BMW X7 xDrive 40i. 

Available Colors: 

1. Phytonic Blue Metallic with Tartufo Brown interior.

2. Mineral White Metallic with Tartufo Brown interior.

Specifications:

• 3.0-liter BMW Twin Power Turbo inline 6-cylinder, xDrive, intelligent all-wheel drive

• 48V mild-hybrid technology.

• Swift-shifting paddle-controlled 8-speed automatic transmission

• 335 hp and 331 lb-ft of torque

• 0-60 mph sprint below six seconds. 

• Ribbed twin-kidney grille, long nose, and broad hood

• Front fascia's lower grille is flanked by big fog lights and C-shaped air intakes

• Seven standard all-electric seats.

• Panoramic Glass Roof and Sky Lounge.

• The dash features twin large screens and organized switches that angle slightly toward the driver. 

• 22" inch Alloy bi-color ferric grey wheels, with all-season run-flat tires.
